data.description: Renovated single family residence in a sought after community just waiting on a family. This is a must see! This cozy one level home is in a duplex community where each unit is individually owned. This home features a brick focal point fireplace as you enter into the living area, nice sized eat-in kitchen with plenty of windows to bird watch during your morning cup of Java. There are 3 generous sized bedroom and 2 updated and tiled bathroom, new carpet and new LVP flooring throughout the home. This yard will enhance family time with room for so many activities. All public information pertaining to the residence and it's size should be verified by the interested parties.
